data.description: LIVE ON VACATION NOW! Start Living the "Florida Dream"    Indulge in the Florida dream lifestyle with this custom-built "MAINTENANCE-FREE" Lee Wetherington home. Welcome to a world of relaxation and convenience where every detail has been meticulously crafted for your enjoyment.    Key Features:    Breathtaking Pond Views: Take in the serene beauty of the oversized screen lanai that offers stunning pond views, creating a tranquil oasis in your backyard.  Immaculate Home: This home is in pristine condition and comes equipped with modern amenities, including a NEW A/C, SOLAR PANELS, GENERATOR, TANKLESS WATER HEATER, and a WATER SOFTENER.  Spacious Lot: Enjoy the luxury of an oversized lot, giving you extra space and privacy.  Tara Preserve: Located in Bradenton, Tara Preserve is often referred to as the "Best-Kept Secret." Discover the allure of this special neighborhood.  Community Highlights:    Heated Community Pool and Spa: Relax and unwind in style.  Tennis Courts and Pickleball: Enjoy active recreation with friends and neighbors.  Community Club House: A gathering place for community events and socializing.  Public Golf Course (NO MEMBERSHIP REQUIRED): Golf enthusiasts will appreciate the convenience of a nearby course.  Low Maintenance Living:  Forget about yard work and upkeep! The LOW HOA fee covers all yard maintenance, mulching, and sprinkler maintenance, as well as cable and internet services. You can truly enjoy a worry-free lifestyle.    Prime Location:  This home's strategic location is unbeatable, with easy access to I75 and over 80 restaurants within a 15-minute drive. Additionally, you're just 30 minutes away from Downtown Sarasota and our World-Famous Powder White Sand Beaches!    CDD Included:  The CDD (Community Development District) fee is included in the taxes, simplifying your financial management.    Seize this opportunity to live the Florida dream in Tara Preserve. Don't miss out—schedule your viewing today and step into the lifestyle you've always imagined!
